ing account.  This would not be processed in Medius, but used for bank reconciliation purposes.  I have a folder created for this specific vendor where these emails are moved for filing.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nLeslie Rodriguez\\\\r\\\\nAccounts Payable Coordinator\\\\t\\\\r\\\\nHillwood, A Perot Company\\\\r\\\\nDirect: 817.224.6343 | Leslie.Rodriguez@Hillwood.com\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n-----Original Message-----\\\\r\\\\nFrom: fnaach@benekeith.com <fnaach@benekeith.com> \\\\r\\\\nSent: Thursday, March 5, 2026 7:05 AM\\\\r\\\\nTo: PropertiesAP <PROPERTIESAP@HILLWOOD.COM>\\\\r\\\\nSubject: 752944/80040277-ACH EzPay Projected Payment\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n \\\\r\\\\nEXTERNAL SENDER: Do not click links or open attachments unless you recognize the sender / content. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nAttached are the projected invoices that have been selected for payment by ACH transmission. The final transmission may vary from this projection and confirming email will be sent with the exact invoices and amounts. These projected funds will be drawn from your account on 03/09/2026. If you have any questions please reply to this email before\\\\r\\\\n2:00 PM on 03/06/2026. Include your name phone number and a brief description of your question and a representative of Ben E Keith will contact you.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nbank of america    Account xxxxxxxx7768\\\\r\\\\n\\",\\n    \\"received_at\\": null,\\n    \\"sender_email\\": \\"/O=EXCHANGELABS/OU=EXCHANGE ADMINISTRATIVE GROUP (FYDIBOHF23SPDLT)/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=46100910A54B4986A8E81BCF969C14DD-PROPERTIESA\\",\\n    \\"sender_name\\": \\"PropertiesAP\\",\\n    \\"subject\\": \\"FW: 752944/80040277-ACH EzPay Projected Payment\\",\\n    \\"transport_headers\\": \\"Received: from SA1PR16MB6242.namprd16.prod.outlook.com (2603:10b6:806:3d1::20)\\\\r\\\\n by CH0PR16MB5298.namprd16.prod.outlook.com with HTTPS; Thu, 5 Mar 2026\\\\r\\\\n 16:11:59 +0000\\\\r\\\\nAuthentication-Results: dkim=none (message not signed)\\\\r\\\\n header.d=none;dmarc=none action=non