ertiesAP <Propertiesap@hillwood.com>\\\\r\\\\nSubject: **Past Due** Invoice R134095 from Regent Services\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nEXTERNAL SENDER: Do not click links or open attachments unless you recognize the sender / content.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nYour invoice is ready! \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nINVOICE # R134095 | Due on Fri, 12/05/2025 \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nBALANCE DUE \\\\r\\\\n$1,318.43\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nDear Customer: \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nYour invoice is attached. Please remit payment at your earliest convenience. If you have any questions, please contact me. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nThank you for your business. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nSincerely, \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nTaylor Prescott \\\\r\\\\nRegent Services \\\\r\\\\n817-984-1761 \\\\r\\\\n817-984-1297 (Fax)\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nIf you receive an email that seems fraudulent, please check with the business owner before paying, or you can forward the email to security@intuit.com <mailto:security@intuit.com>  so we can look into it. Read more at security.intuit.com.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPowered by QuickBooks\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\u00a9 2025 Intuit, Inc. All rights reserved.\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPrivacy <https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/links.notification.intuit.com/ls/click?upn=u001.ZgeO7sKC-2B9ve0zg-2FufUiEEN7fV9g6OeaOieRNa-2F4DYtAv6IFDzcabX-2FjJpBIDWM9Zqc1_HlvFVcNfIxh7JbwZiTN3OsmMri8WyYLxnnVyPRJaMyi83GNQ3IBktTfEtKW-2BhsbXPrPafXFtyWSeTJrkQUyfGfmmHb2qKJ1Bcp030hJyjLbTpdJwSo72LUIvMsgZFM1Ys3bsu1jGxi719liagdfSU-2F2GOFqDl-2F-2BHOdT1ltavNG1LficKGPmMhlnbhnITLvaepoo1UHAWJ0oV4gZAnAz5QD9so4EIYDfC8TCLKN5saEoBSGUBghINBe-2FDsxEC5iJ3BuAiQFDBPpsSHLY1YKyyxgJcLUFl-2BUtFKpWaVSCPo5poL3E7H88vIwEsg-2F-2BpFvdS54-2BqLhV7c7HShcr6e5Z8EWEWQf59Xbv1BgtRglq4VwRKTdfxH6qnd9foQgO-2F9-2BEMpm-2BQHvh3BOehhCD5OPZBqCEgTHXxAVzYrrkl003DpzC59oU3lK-2BgBRP76Bvn-2FyhX-2B3ZrURaRd70Rr5SZdx2ARoVx4Q3sixLkyAldZUNYD2-2FmINBTyc